### Crear usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Listar usuarios (paginado)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Buscar usuarios por texto (username o email)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=john
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener usuario por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Actualizar usuario (incluye isActive opcional)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_updated",
  "email": "john_updated@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "isActive": true
}

### Desactivar usuario (solo isActive)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### Eliminar usuario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
